# Copy to `.env` only if your tooling loads it. Most wiki gates use `make` targets and
# inline environment variables instead of a dotenv file.
#
# --- LLM Wiki Manager (multi-repo fork-delta; see schema/wiki-manager.md) ---
# Optional: sibling LLM Wiki Base Model checkout used as upstream diff left side.
# When unset, fork-delta compares this manager checkout against each child.
# WIKI_MANAGER_COMPARE_ROOT=/absolute/path/to/LLM Wiki Base Model
#
# Single-child make fork-delta / fork-delta-full instead of env (same semantics as --compare-root):
# make fork-delta CHILD='/abs/child' COMPARE='/abs/LLM Wiki Base Model'
# WIKI_MANAGER_CHILD_SHAOLIN=/absolute/path/to/Shaolin Monastery Research System
# WIKI_MANAGER_CHILD_TAI_PAN=/absolute/path/to/Tai-Pan Wiki
#
# Example (one machine, all four trees under Downloads): after exporting the four paths,
# run `make wiki-manager-refresh-dry` then `make wiki-manager-snapshot` (see schema/wiki-manager.md).
#
# Forwarded to `scripts/validate_wiki.py` when set for `make wiki-validate` / `wiki-check` / `wiki-ci`, `scripts/autopilot.py`, or nested calls from `scripts/daemon.py`
# (same semantics as documented in README).
# VALIDATE_WIKI_ARGS=--strict-citation-meta
#
# Inventory external URLs without HTTP probes (air-gapped / CI-adjacent workflows).
# WIKI_EXTERNAL_LINKS_SKIP_PROBE=1
#
# Max characters of stdout/stderr retained per autopilot step in status/ops JSON (256–500000).
# When unset, successful steps keep 2000 and failing steps keep 16000. Daemon heartbeat uses the same helper (scripts/wiki_paths.py autopilot_log_tail_chars).
# AUTOPILOT_LOG_TAIL_CHARS=8000
